        "sourceMode": "inline",
        "sourceHtml": "<!doctype html>\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <style>\n      body {\n        margin: 0;\n        min-height: 100vh;\n        display: grid;\n        place-items: center;\n        font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif;\n        background: #f8fafc;\n        color: #0f172a;\n      }\n      article {\n        width: min(420px, calc(100vw - 48px));\n        padding: 24px;\n        border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;\n        border-radius: 16px;\n        background: #ffffff;\n        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgb(15 23 42 / 0.08);\n      }\n      h1 {\n        margin: 0 0 12px;\n        font-size: 28px;\n        line-height: 1.1;\n      }\n      p {\n        margin: 0 0 16px;\n        color: #475569;\n        line-height: 1.5;\n      }\n      button {\n        border: 0;\n        border-radius: 9999px;\n        padding: 10px 16px;\n        font: inherit;\n        color: #ffffff;\n        background: #2563eb;\n      }\n    </style>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <article class=\"card\">\n      <h1>Hello</h1>\n      <p>Bridge verification target</p>\n      <button class=\"cta\">Click</button>\n    </article>\n  </body>\n</html>",
